      <div class="section-header fade-up">
        <span class="section-tag">Why Tundrex</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Nature's Most Potent Probiotic,<br/>Delivered to You</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle" style="margin:0 auto;">
          Not all probiotics are equal. Tundrex goes deeper — sourcing strains that evolved to survive 
          extreme conditions, making them exponentially more resilient and effective in your body.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="why-grid">
        <div class="why-card fade-up delay-1">
          <div class="why-icon">
            <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="3 18 12 4 21 18"/><line x1="3" y1="18" x2="21" y2="18"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="12" y2="8"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Siberian Soil Sourced</h3>
          <p>Our <em>Bacillus subtilis</em> strains are extracted from pristine organic tundra soil in Siberia — one of the most untouched, mineral-rich environments on Earth.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card fade-up delay-2">
          <div class="why-icon">
            <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="23 6 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 1 18"/><polyline points="17 6 23 6 23 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Higher CFU Count</h3>
          <p>Each capsule delivers a higher concentration of viable, spore-forming bacteria than conventional probiotics — surviving stomach acid to colonize where it matters.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card fade-up delay-3">
          <div class="why-icon">
            <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Doctor Endorsed</h3>
          <p>Trusted by Dr. Leo Galland, MD — a leading integrative medicine physician in New York — who considers <em>Bacillus subtilis</em> the finest probiotic organism he's worked with.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card fade-up delay-4">
          <div class="why-icon">
            <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M11 20A7 7 0 0118 9h1a8 8 0 01-8 11z"/><path d="M5 12a7 7 0 014-6.3"/><line x1="2" y1="22" x2="11" y2="13"/></svg>
